    "To predict y t-1 directly during the denoising stage, we employ a technique akin to that used in 13, 14.",
    "First, the model G is trained for denoising to estimate the value of y ′ 0 after we feed the source image x, the noisy image y t, the temporal variable t, and z into it.",
